IMAPAccount fb
Host outlook.office365.com
User guro@fb.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup user guro@fb.com domain outlook.office365.com"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore fb-remote
Account fb

MaildirStore fb-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/fb/
Inbox ~/.mail/fb/Inbox

Channel fb
Master :fb-remote:
Slave :fb-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *